snippet: After steering clear of the campaign trail for most of 2014, President Barack Obama is stepping up his efforts with a pair of events to boost Democrats running for governor in Maryland and Illinois....

headline.print_headline: Obama to Campaign for Dems in Maryland, Illinois
headline.main: Obama to Campaign for Dems in Maryland, Illinois

lead_paragraph: After steering clear of the campaign trail for most of 2014, President Barack Obama is stepping up his efforts with a pair of events to boost Democrats running for governor in Maryland and Illinois.
